\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Former Olympic champion\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"a unanimous assessment\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's slippery, it's quite loose and quite wide.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you go fast it's super slippery,\\\" Schurter said.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schurter\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope the gravel still goes a bit to the side and makes it less loose everywhere.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gravel\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can feel there was no mountain biking before and it's 100% man-made, like we saw in London and in Rio.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999990050128, \"rank\": 9.553688581531483e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.828945896634137, \"rank\": 0.20635134820498935, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It could be a bit more natural, but in general, it's nice.\\\"\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The topDutch hopeful Puck Pietersealready did a full preview of the course last year ahead of the test event, so she knew what to expect but also noted the dry nature of the circuit will force riders to be comfortable with a little drift in the turns.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_puck\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.182633127012339e-21, \"text\": \"Puck\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_puck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_puck\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full preview\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the test event\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the dry nature\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"the circuit\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"a little drift\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"the turns\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's good.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, we already had the chance to familiarise with the course and race here.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1513}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have made some small adjustments, but for the main part it's the same,\\\" Pieterse said.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some small adjustments\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"the main part\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"Pieterse\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of gravel, which is slippery, especially in the corners, so you have to be careful.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"gravel\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"the corners\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a course in which you have to be able to take a lot of speed into the corners and you should not be afraid to drift a little on the slippery surface.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a course\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"the corners\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"the slippery surface\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The technical parts come quickly after each other but it's not such a long lap and there is no long three- to four-minute climb because all climbs are interrupted with little things,\\\" she said, adding, \\\"You have to be good on any course.\\\"\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The technical parts\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"such a long lap\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"four-minute climb\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"all climbs\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"little things\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"any course\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest race content\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"reviews\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"expert buying guides\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pieterse expectedPauline Ferrand Pr\\u00e9votto be the top contender on her home turf.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pieterse\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"expectedPauline Ferrand Pr\\u00e9votto\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the top contender\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"her home turf\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's in her home country, she's the top favourite, so that will put the pressure on, but it can also give her wings.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her home country\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"her wings\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will find out on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel as if I did everything I could, so that gives me a lot of confidence.\\\"\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British ridersTom Pidcock- one of the topmen's Olympic MTB favouritesas defending champion - and Evie Richards were not as bullish about the course, with Pidcock giving quite a blunt assessment.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2534, \"end\": 2541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9996778861631758, \"rank\": 0.0003221232572869422, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2631, \"end\": 2644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\", \"score\": 0.9999999329952538, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evie Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the topmen's Olympic MTB favouritesas\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"champion\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a blunt assessment\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not the best course in the world but it's the same for everyone,\\\" Pidcock said.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best course\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's bland and I think they could have done a better job of making a more mountain bike course.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better job\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"a more mountain bike course\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love mountain biking for the reasons that drive us to enjoy it.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"the reasons\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the courses you get to ride, the places you get to go to.\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the courses\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you just gravel over a nice hillside, it's not really mountain biking.\\\"\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nice hillside\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3087}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pidcock and Richards agreed that the course is less tactical than the ones they encounter during the season.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not much thinking to go into either.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much thinking\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's kind of one line you just go down,\\\" Pidcock said.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one line\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3302}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is just one line.\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just one line\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Normally you can choose different lines,\\\" Richards said before adding, \\\"It's still technical because they have got lots of cool features, drops and jumps, but it's man-made.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different lines\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3412}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3481}, {\"ngram\": \"cool features\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"jumps\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just one line, and you race that line.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just one line\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3554}, {\"ngram\": \"that line\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's probably easier to learn, but just less choices when you come to race.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just less choices\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think they have done the best they have done.\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being as close as Paris, it's not the easiest thing to just pop up a mountain bike course anywhere.\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3724, \"end\": 3729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.433186762568366e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the easiest thing\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3757}, {\"ngram\": \"a mountain bike course\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I was a designer, I'd like a lot more natural features rather than man-made.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a designer\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3825}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot more natural features\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I think we normally see that at the Olympic Games, it's normally a bit of a different course than what we'd normally race at World Cups.\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 4028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3941}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3962}, {\"ngram\": \"a different course\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3984}, {\"ngram\": \"World Cups\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are normally in the Alps, somewhere, somewhere in a nice ski resort and this is super close to the city centre.\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Alps\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4056}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice ski resort\", \"from\": 4082, \"to\": 4099}, {\"ngram\": \"the city centre\", \"from\": 4127, \"to\": 4142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think they have done the best job of what they can do.\\\"\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best job\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dull course aside, Richards is excited to represent Britain at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4203, \"to\": 4284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4255, \"end\": 4262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9987631121448104, \"rank\": 0.0012384195265210997, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Richards\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4230}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4266, \"to\": 4283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics is all I ever dreamt of and that's why I got into sport.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4299}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 4350, \"to\": 4355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the age of six, it was all I wanted to do.\", \"from\": 4357, \"to\": 4405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not just for me, but for my family, for my grandparents, it's what we have all ever dreamt of.\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fa